document.full_text: yemen's ambassador to the united nations abdullah alsaidi has resigned, the latest high-ranking member of president ali abdullah saleh's government to quit in protest against the killing of dozens of demonstrators.
document.title: yemen's u.n. envoy quits over violence to protesters
